commit d4357207c043d54e9caa7ee075ef00cbe8dae0c0
Author: Marios Trivyzas <matriv@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Jun 25 14:05:40 2024 +0300

    Fixed nullability for `format_type` scalar
    
    The 2nd argument is ignored, so even if it's `null` the function can
    return `???` as a result (only based on the 1st argument.
    
    Fixes: #16225

